The Linux Foundation and the projects we support form the most ambitious and
successful investment in the creation of shared technology

Largest Shared Technology Investment

   The Linux Foundation supports the creation of sustainable open source
   ecosystems by providing financial and intellectual resources,
   infrastructure, services, events, and training.

16B USD

   Estimated development cost of the 100+ world’s leading projects hosted
   at The Linux Foundation

35,000

   Technologists attend our events annually, from more than 11,000
   companies and 113 countries

1 Million

   Open source professionals have enrolled in our free open source
   training courses

10 / 10

   Largest cloud service providers are Linux Foundation project
   contributors and members
