     it: Apple, Facebook, Google, IBM, Intel, Microsoft, GitHub, Netflix,
     Red Hat, Slack, and The Linux Foundation.
     SD Times2017 100 Influencers

   “

     We’ve been one of the bedrock members of The Linux Foundation since
     its inception. We have a long history of doing open source projects
     throughout many communities. (But) there are things we couldn’t do
     before that we can now do, working in partnership with The Linux
     Foundation. If we were to take a project, open source it ourselves,
     and expect people to come to that project, that’s a very difficult
     path. But when you do it in partnership with The Linux Foundation,
     that path gets smoothed.
     Todd MooreVP of Open Technology at IBM

   “

     The Linux Foundation is home to Linux, Node.js and other mission
